                      </p>
                      <p class="lead">In minutes you can make hundreds of choices. So steal those precious moments when you are standing in line at the 7-Eleven or lying in bed while your partner is snoring! Then, when you have extra 30 minutes or $60, Listpick, can remind you that those new shoes are really your top priority. (Or maybe it's vacuuming the cat hair off the sofa.) With Lipstick, your priorities rise above the noise.</p>
